<h4 id="2-spring-service">2. Spring @Service</h4>
<ul>
  <li>@Service μ–΄λ…Έν…μ΄μ…μ€ νΉλ³„ν™” λ @Component μ–΄λ…Έν…μ΄μ…μ΄λ‹¤.</li>
